text: "That Girl" is a 2006 song made by American singer Frankie J and American rappers Mannie Fresh and Chamillionaire. It was released from Frankie J's album Priceless (2006). Mannie Fresh, Chamillionaire and Play-N-Skillz wrote the song. It was number 100 on the Billboard Hot 100 on August 17, 2006, at number 100, It went to number 43 on October 7. ==References== Category:Chamillionaire songs Category:Songs written by Chamillionaire Category:2006 songs
title: That Girl (Frankie J song)
